@Node WhatIsIt "DiskMate/WhatIsIt"

 

			*---- DiskMate V4.0 ---------*


		        * Multitasking

                        * Multi drive Diskcopier Dos/NonDos

                        * Multi drive Disk formatter

                        * Multi drive Disk eraser

                        * Disk Installer

                        * Floppy disk Checker
		
			* Floppy disk Cruncher (DMS)

